file.name: license-component.openapi.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: License Component
  description: Component
  version: 1.0.0

paths: {}

components:
  schemas:
    MultipleLicense:
      required:
        - total
        - licenses
      properties:
        total:
          format: int64
          type: integer
        licenses:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/License'
    License:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
          nullable: true
        issued_at:
          type: string
        expires_at:
          type: string
        subscription:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Subscription'
    Subscription:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        owner:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/SubscriptionOwner'
        items:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/SubscriptionItem'
        provider_id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
          description: UUID形式
        quantity:
          type: integer
        unit:
          type: string
        license_type:
          type: string
          enum: [ Corporation, User, Device, Assignless ]
        status:
          type: string
          enum: [ active, inactive, suspend ]
        purchased_at:
          type: string
          description: ISO8601
        issued_at:
          type: string
          description: ISO8601
        expires_at:
          type: string
          description: ISO8601
    SubscriptionOwner:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
          enum: [ Corporation, User ]
          description: |
            Corporation: 企業
            User: ユーザー
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
    SubscriptionItem:
      type: object
      properties:
        item_id:
          type: string
        plan_id:
          type: string
